            <title>[HBASE-4631] Cleanup and optimize embedded HRegionThriftServer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4631</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There were some good comments in the review of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4460&quot; title=&quot;Support running an embedded ThriftServer within a RegionServer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4460&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4460&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

